      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Created作为入口状态。那Created之后有哪些分支？是直接开始工作，还是有可能被取消？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "InProgress",
        "Cancelled"
