    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Created有两个主要出口：一个是Start Work进入InProgress，另一个是Cancel直接进入Cancelled。这两个都是合理的业务场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "InProgress",
        "Cancelled",
        "Start Work",
        "Cancel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Created到InProgress和Cancelled的连接已添加。现在处理InProgress，这个状态应该比较复杂吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
